description: Crumbed hoki is the hero in this Mexican favourite. Then simply top with kaleslaw and chunky salsa.

name: Fast Fish Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Line a baking tray with baking paper.
Place fish fillets on prepared tray, and bake for 18 minutes, or until golden, turning halfway through cooking. Cut fillets in half to make strips.
Meanwhile, in a large bowl, prepare kaleslaw kit according to packet instructions.
Remove freshness sachets from tortillas. Microwave tortillas, in the packet, for 25 seconds. Fill warm tortillas with kaleslaw and crumbed fish strips and top with salsa to serve.
